   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:span text:style-name="Strong_20_Emphasis"/></text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:span text:style-name="Strong_20_Emphasis">Conclusion</text:span></text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">The SGC appl<text:span text:style-name="T6">ies</text:span> object-oriented design principles and provides a CLI for interacting with data. The system is efficient, extensible, and user-friendly, with clear separation of concerns between data handling, business logic, and user interaction.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">Testing confirmed that the system behaves correctly under both valid and invalid inputs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>